Hi guys , welcome to Thyview Comments . Naa Peru Sharath , Thyview Subscriber . And Here is my non spoiler Review of MissIndia ! Meeru movie choodataniki , ee comment motham chadavaala ante , ippude cheptunna , 75 % general audience ( time pass kosam movie choose vallaki ) ee movie nachadu . 1st half aithe , edho parledhu baane undi anipinchinaa , 2nd half bedisikottindhi . Aa chai ni America lo ela sell chestundi , ela top position ki vastundi ani chaala sepu wait chesa . Jagapathi babu ela challenge chestaaru ani baaga excite ayya . Kaani akkada 2 challenges maatrame untai . Avi kooda antha impact iyyaledhu . Movie motham lo naaku istamaindhi , cameraman maatrame ! Theatrical experience theppinchaadu ! Hatsoff ! Malli , women powerment dialogs kooda over gaa untadhi . Aa dialogs vinte satisfied kaavadam atu unchithe . Ammailu vinte inkaa pogaru gaa aipothaaru . Abbailu aithe mandipothaaru . Avi aadavaallu em thakkuva kaaru ani kaakundaa , magaadu chaep aadadhanikante , anelaa untai . Meeru , ee movie inkaa choosindaka pothe assalu choodadhu ! Final gaa ee movie ki naa rating 2.5 / 5 Thank You guys , See you again !

@Ravi Kiran Vedula that ’ s what I mean , like these “ inspirational ” movies often dramatize the characters , like you said . For example , they ’ ll make the main lead extra hard working and overly moral and make them unrealistically good . And they ’ ll make the villains unrealistically bad with all these traits . It makes the movie very shallow and boring for me cause most of them are this way . And the story won ’ t even be different . Same story , main lead has idea , some bad guys opposes , she does it anyways fails somehow and wants to give up , someone gives her a lecture to not give up , she does something and wins . and in between there ’ s some love story . This movie was geared to inspire women , so all these things will be about women empowerment somehow . Haven ’ t seen it but I bet even she gives a speech at the end about women . Similar to Srimanthudu / Maharishi , where Mahesh Babu is overly good and everything about the movie is geared towards giving back . If I remember he gives a speech I ’ m that too . That ’ s what I meant bro . Like , all these inspirational movie feel the same to me and feel routine and not entertaining and old format , and since this movie is specifically geared to inspire women that ’ s why I said that .
